      "writtenOn": "2018-11-27T20:29:13Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I see, so you believe that CTFontCreateWithFontDescriptor was buggy or not fully documented already in macOS 10.11 with regard to kCTFontSymbolicTrait, but CTFontCreateCopyWithSymbolicTraits seems to work ok. I could believe that the code is written such that it\u0027s basically impossible or non obvious to create a correct CTFontSymbolicTraits value without starting with an existing CTFontSymbolicTraits value from an existing CTFont.",
      "parentUuid": "332c22cb_b8feeb19",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 815,
